race.comment: TUMBY BAY (1) missed the frame last time when fourth (18.55) at this track but prior to that had two placings in a row. Solid record at the distance winning two races. Better than the latest run and deserves another chance. OUR INSPIRATION (7) led throughout to score two back then drifted back and missed the frame latest finishing a 4.5 lengths 4th at this track (29.98). Must be included in calculations. CALLA OREO (6) broke a string of placings finishing in the money five on end before a last start sixth (23.42) at this track. Form at the trip sound including two wins. His last run is a proven strong form reference. Has ability and a bold showing is expected. SATRIANI (4) looks an each-way chance.
